{"tid":1995953,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"講真「天馬」(PEGASUS)一睇就知係掃黃行動代號嚟","createTime":"2020-04-30T15:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T04:04:28.000Z","uid":7439,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"edbec21de544c0132140a5a151e3a819a9872b59","tid":1995953,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:48:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直至九十年代，很多行動都習慣性使用代號，其實很多時是不需要，只是時尚和看似專業，亦方便傳媒朋友，因他們一般會問甚麼行動代號。<br />\n  另外亦有一些是時常使用，一聽見命令行動乜乜，大家便明白怎樣做，例如一些行動是專門攔截賊車，而亦有一些定期行動，都用同一個名，同事一聽便知甚麼時候便有甚麼行動。<br />\n  因行動名稱仍以英文為主，如中文譯名能用上一些較貼近行動目的的意譯，加上中文的博大精深，如能掌握其精髓就更有意思了！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1758711/org/0ebe2b8323f94aa856bee50f27fe1ea3.jpg/UpBXPNQgz8wtP6LhUsOO9b0O3h2f1Pfcb-LThG_i04Q?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1758711%2Forg%2F0ebe2b8323f94aa856bee50f27fe1ea3.jpg%2FUpBXPNQgz8wtP6LhUsOO9b0O3h2f1Pfcb-LThG_i04Q%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=042e079c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20181121/photo/1121-00176-056b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181121%2Fphoto%2F1121-00176-056b1.jpg&h=100450db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一眼分得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n「萬里達」(MILESMETER)<br />\n「孤影」(LONESHADOW)<br />\n「犁庭掃穴」(LEVINGTON)<br />\n「火石」（FLINTSTONE）<br />\n「冠軍」（CHAMPION）<br />\n「烽火」（FIRESTORM）<br />\n「虎尾」（TIGERTAIL）<br />\n「角力」（RANGEPOWER）<br />\n「激雷」（THUNDERKICK）<br />\n「雷霆18」（THUNDERBOLT 18）<br />\n「激流」（UPPERRUN）<br />\n「天馬」（PEGASUS）<br />\n「領馬」（LANDMASTER）<br />\n「勁躍」（POWERHOP）<br />\n「搜鷁」（STEMPICKER）<br />\n「堯天」（GOLDENAGE）<br />\n「水戰」（SPLASHWAR）"},{"pid":"800fca0b6774db53d65f9b3afb22f670bd1644a0","tid":1995953,"uid":7439,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T15:50:16.000Z","msg":"入境處仲